summary: An ordinance relating to alcoholic liquors; regulating and licensing the sale, disposal and liquors; prohibiting the sale, disposal or distribution of any such liquors containing more than sixteen percentum (16%) of alcohol by weight; defining offenses; prescribing penalites; amending Sections 2 and 11 of Ordinance No. 63561 and repealing Ordinance No. 63637 and declaring an emergency.
